'''Ophelia Piner''' (October 22, 2012 - December 2, 2111) was an American professional basketball player in the WNBA. 

==Early life and education==
Piner was born in Houston, Texas to Diana (1977 - 2051) and Cooper Piner (1978 - 2063). Her mother was a school administrator and her father was a marine biologist. She had an older brother, Steven (1999 - 2075), a grocer for Henderson Foods, and a Cavalier King Charles spaniel named Lanika (d. 2025). 

